  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<h1 class=\"size-48 is-title1-48 is-title-bold\">2023 AMC 華人之冠<br />\n獵豹締造大滿貫</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:28px;\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><em><strong>許庭誠(建中G10) AMC12B: 150（滿分）<br />\n馬宇辰(衛道G8) AMC10A: 150（滿分）<br />\n林秉坤(南山G8) AMC8:25（滿分）</strong></em></span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">AMC（美國數學競賽）是全球參與度最高的中學生數學競賽之一，也是美國選拔IMO選手的第一階段賽事。<br />\n<br />\n它的題目設計多出自著名大學專家之手，靈活多變具創意與趣味。<br />\n<br />\nAMC雖然屬於初階賽，但題目的難度隨題號增加，尤其AMC10/12試題在深水區（P20-25)很具挑戰性，而且在75分鐘的時間限制下，要獲取高分 （超過120分）相當不容易。<br />\n<br />\n近年由於難度的提升，甚至對許多奧數選手在AMC12要超過140分，也非易事！<br />\n<br />\n獵豹三位高手以過人的稟賦和刻苦努力，技壓群雄獲得了滿分，殊為難得，也替台灣增光！獵豹得英才教之 與有榮焉。</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\"><img src=\"pic/elite/cheetah-elite-122-body-1.jpg\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><strong>參與課程：</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n許庭誠：<br />\nFUC微積分,FS高中輕競賽,FA高階賽,國中GM(獵豹x寰宇)<br />\n馬宇辰<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">：</span><br />\nFUC微積分, 國中數學+輕競賽J+FJ 7~9, 高中數學S, AMC10衝刺, AIME衝刺班<br />\n林秉坤<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">：</span><br />\n高中數學S ,FS高中輕競賽, Sci資優自然, AMC10衝刺, AIME衝刺班,國中GM(獵豹x寰宇)<br />\n---<br />\n<strong>與學長們一起學習,歡迎參加：</strong><br />\n<strong>「獵豹高等數學系列：微積分 FUC2」</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1392434058375942/?__cft__[0]=AZVi7NNaAgAuUaD5pEkhG5bfiN-CVJqOdwuZ4M2s_pooEtMkVzGtYe5X4oN2U9YAjqwlZCrJ4qbaFYiDx04pT1hcLcAn7bAgLby2ClqT1irmxVly_fMvMX9Cjldp-trGC2i5ZkObOHABHUvLA0j2ym3EM5V-D47j01nSdfR1wv1yyNiFWqAS3LID52xgm8kHmGItk2jCr52rhGx-IfMv_WpD&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/....../permalink/1392434058375942/</a><br />\n<br />\n2401PK1/2/3B,<br />\n2312PK4B,2312PK3D 開跑<br />\n<strong>「獵豹小學 3~6年級PK系列 (下學期) 課程 開跑了!」</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1389019518717396/?mibextid=uJjRxr&amp;__cft__[0]=AZVi7NNaAgAuUaD5pEkhG5bfiN-CVJqOdwuZ4M2s_pooEtMkVzGtYe5X4oN2U9YAjqwlZCrJ4qbaFYiDx04pT1hcLcAn7bAgLby2ClqT1irmxVly_fMvMX9Cjldp-trGC2i5ZkObOHABHUvLA0j2ym3EM5V-D47j01nSdfR1wv1yyNiFWqAS3LID52xgm8kHmGItk2jCr52rhGx-IfMv_WpD&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/....../1389019518717396/......</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>『獵豹國中數學課程開跑！』</strong><br />\n課綱資優進度或備考課程:J72A七(下)/J82A八(下)/J92A九(下)<br />\n輕競賽專題課程:FJ72七(下)/FJ82八(下)<br />\n會考非選與素養題高手訓練課程:JE92<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1382698096016205/?mibextid=uJjRxr&amp;__cft__[0]=AZVi7NNaAgAuUaD5pEkhG5bfiN-CVJqOdwuZ4M2s_pooEtMkVzGtYe5X4oN2U9YAjqwlZCrJ4qbaFYiDx04pT1hcLcAn7bAgLby2ClqT1irmxVly_fMvMX9Cjldp-trGC2i5ZkObOHABHUvLA0j2ym3EM5V-D47j01nSdfR1wv1yyNiFWqAS3LID52xgm8kHmGItk2jCr52rhGx-IfMv_WpD&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/....../1382698096016205/......</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>『獵豹S102高一(下)、S112高二(下)』開跑!』</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1376099730009375/?mibextid=zDhOQc&amp;__cft__[0]=AZVi7NNaAgAuUaD5pEkhG5bfiN-CVJqOdwuZ4M2s_pooEtMkVzGtYe5X4oN2U9YAjqwlZCrJ4qbaFYiDx04pT1hcLcAn7bAgLby2ClqT1irmxVly_fMvMX9Cjldp-trGC2i5ZkObOHABHUvLA0j2ym3EM5V-D47j01nSdfR1wv1yyNiFWqAS3LID52xgm8kHmGItk2jCr52rhGx-IfMv_WpD&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/....../1376099730009375/......</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「Sci12國中資優化學, Sci22高一資優物理 報名開跑！」</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1370122890607059/?__cft__[0]=AZVi7NNaAgAuUaD5pEkhG5bfiN-CVJqOdwuZ4M2s_pooEtMkVzGtYe5X4oN2U9YAjqwlZCrJ4qbaFYiDx04pT1hcLcAn7bAgLby2ClqT1irmxVly_fMvMX9Cjldp-trGC2i5ZkObOHABHUvLA0j2ym3EM5V-D47j01nSdfR1wv1yyNiFWqAS3LID52xgm8kHmGItk2jCr52rhGx-IfMv_WpD&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/....../permalink/1370122890607059/</a><br />\n--<br />\n想了解有潛力的孩子如何從小學開始在獵豹原植自己的實力，本週日早上,宗翰老師主講,PK直播講座加場：<br />\n報名按讚留言+1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/N4ep5gQAM7W6dkE9/?mibextid=K35XfP&amp;__cft__[0]=AZVi7NNaAgAuUaD5pEkhG5bfiN-CVJqOdwuZ4M2s_pooEtMkVzGtYe5X4oN2U9YAjqwlZCrJ4qbaFYiDx04pT1hcLcAn7bAgLby2ClqT1irmxVly_fMvMX9Cjldp-trGC2i5ZkObOHABHUvLA0j2ym3EM5V-D47j01nSdfR1wv1yyNiFWqAS3LID52xgm8kHmGItk2jCr52rhGx-IfMv_WpD&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/share/N4ep5gQAM7W6dkE9/......</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n詳見以下臉書連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/rVNTJhukqU6E87YP/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/share/p/rVNTJhukqU6E87YP/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<h1 class=\"size-64 is-title1-64 is-title-bold\">&nbsp;</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
